text: Antoni Kazimierz Pacyński (born 29 May 1943) is a Polish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Biography at olimpijski.pl Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Jarosław Category:Sportspeople from Podkarpackie Voivodeship
